)abbrev package PCOMP PolynomialComposition
++ Description:
++ This package \undocumented
PolynomialComposition(UP: UnivariatePolynomialCategory(R), R: Ring): with
        compose: (UP, UP) -> UP
                ++ compose(p,q) \undocumented
    == add
        compose(g, h) ==
            r: UP := 0
            while g ~= 0 repeat
                r := leadingCoefficient(g)*h**degree(g) + r
                g := reductum g
            r

